  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Network Watcher模块的架构图，核心是展示Azure订阅内部的网络拓扑，以及它和本地数据中心、互联网的连接关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "Network Watcher",
        "On-Prem",
        "Internet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Azure内部需要细化到什么程度？我看到有Resource Group、VNet、Subnets这些层级，是要全部展开吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Resource Group",
        "VNet",
        "Subnets"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Azure这部分用子图包起来，里面放三层：Resource Group作为容器，VNet标注10.10.0.0/16网段，Subnets里面写web/app/db/mgmt四个子网。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "Resource Group",
        "VNet",
        "Subnets"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，Azure子图已经画好了。那外部连接呢？On-Prem和互联网的位置怎么摆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "OnPrem",
        "Internet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "On-Prem放在Azure子图左边，标注成VyOS路由器加虚拟机；Internet放右边。VNet和两边都要有连线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPrem",
        "Internet",
        "VNet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "连线的样式有讲究吗？比如On-Prem到VNet是VPN还是专线？Internet到VNet是单向还是双向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPrem",
        "Internet",
        "VNet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "On-Prem到VNet用双向箭头，表示VPN连接；Internet到VNet用单向箭头，表示从互联网流入的流量。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPrem",
        "Internet",
        "VNet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。不过我发现On-Prem的标注你写的是\"VyOS + VMs\"，需要把加号换成文字\"和\"吗，还是保持技术符号？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPrem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保持\"VyOS + VMs\"就行，这是标准写法。对了，VNet的标注前面要加\"VNet:\"前缀，网段用10.10.0.0/16。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VNet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新。再确认下Subnets的写法，是\"Subnets: web/app/db/mgmt\"这样吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Subnets"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Subnets前面不需要引号包裹整个字符串，直接写就行。还有On-Prem的完整标注应该是\"On-Prem (VyOS + VMs)\"，带上括号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Subnets",
        "OnPrem"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修复完成。现在整个图结构是：Azure子图包含RG、VNet、Subnets三层，外部左侧On-Prem通过双向箭头连VNet，右侧Internet通过单向箭头连VNet。符合Network Watcher的监控视角了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "Resource Group",
        "VNet",
        "Subnets",
        "OnPrem",
        "Internet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这就是Module 18要的Network Watcher流量图。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "Network Watcher",
        "flowchart"
      ],
